#

Honey Mustard Glazed Salmon with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$18.99
600 kcal

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodComfort FoodEasy to Make

Description

A succulent salmon fillet glazed with sweet honey mustard, served alongside creamy garlic mashed potatoes, making for a delightful and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Salmon Fillet: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Dijon Mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Potatoes: 4 large, peeled and diced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Chives: for garnish
